nds clasped around the bent knee to the level of pressure desired (gas trapped in the large intestine may be released in this asana).  The other leg is extended straight and the gaze is natural and forward.</p></li></ul><ul><li><h5>Benefits:</h5><p class='text'>Releases gas trapped in large intestine.  Stretches the cervical spine (neck).  Improves the digestion system.  Aides in elimination.</p></li></ul></section>        </section>

